Through the ''[[What's The Story?]]'' feature of [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace: The Official ''Star Wars'' Fan Club]], '''Billy Buehler''' named and wrote the backstory for the character of [[Corla Metonae/Legends|Corla Metonae]] in the [[Databank (original)|Databank]], as well as naming and co-writing the backstory of the [[Unstable Terrain Artillery Transport/Legends|Unstable Terrain Artillery Transport]]. He also added some finishing touches to [[Olana Chion/Legends|Olana Chion's]] entry. Buehler is partially responsible for the fandom cult status of the [[Whiphid/Legends|Whiphid]] [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[K'Kruhk]] and his "freakin' sweet" hat, as well as suggesting the popular unofficial nickname of [[Vongerella]] for the unnamed female Yuuzhan Vong mentioned in the [[Dark Forces Saga]]. He is a ''[[Jedi Council Forums]]'' Literature moderator, posting as ''The2ndQuest''. His alias is ''The2ndquest'' on [[StarWars.com]] and "the2ndquest" on the [[Dark Horse Comics]] website. He also created the logo for [[W:c:swfans:Fleet Junkie|Fleet Junkies]] and provided their battle cry.

